title: Iran Claims Missile Attack on Iraq That Sent U.S. Troops Rushing for Shelter - The Wall Street Journal
content: Iran Claims Missile Attack on Iraq That Sent U.S. Troops Rushing for Shelter  The Wall Street JournalView Full Coverage on Google News
description: The statement came hours after U.S. officials said missiles originating from Iran struck in the vicinity of a new American consulate under construction in northern Iraq.
